fields.Action: Boot the DUT and Check the IPv6 Wan traces.
fields.Expected Result:
A DHCPv6 Cycle is triggered after boot and DUT obtains an IPv6 prefix.

	DUT LAN  interface is presents a IPv6 address. (ifconfig bridge)
	Eg,  inet6 addr: 2001:470:cb76:2000::100/64

fields.Action: From a LAN PC with Pure IPv6 connectivity(No IPv4 enabled on it). Try to check it's connectivity.
fields.Expected Result:
The LAN PC obtains an IPv6 IP address and its possible to surf the internet using IPv6 (e.g. ipv6.google.com)

	DNS resolution and packets uses IPv6 addresses.

fields.description:
[Precondition]

	Wan is UP with IPv6 on Wan Available.
